TEXT 2360 -1920 Left 2 ;parasitics are capacitance/inductance/resistance\npassive components are capacitor/inductor/resistor\nhigh and low side elements have [H] and [L] appended to name\nG_CC = common reference voltage, phase output etc.\nGD = gate drive\nG = gate\nD = drain\nS = source
